<br>
I have had enchanters make hot keys annocing what mobs they have mezzed and have the message in Caps and spam it a couple of times to make sure the group sees it.<br>
<br>
But as one of the other mages pointed out the best key to pet control is paying attention. <p><p><font color="#0000FF">Crispinskyhawke<br>
